     ===========================

     See UTKLDocDB-doc-780 for a description of this software

     === To compile ===
     $ mkdir build
     $ cd build
     $ cmake -DROOT_HOME=<ROOT system> ..
     $ make

     === Running ===
     Once compiled return back to main directory (cd ..) from previous step
     execute with:
     $ bin/crmt